Available Resources &amp; Human Rights:</i> <i>Analytical Report</i>, Center for Women&#8217;s Global Leadership, 
June 2011. See also the reports of the Independent Expert on the effects of foreign debt and other 
related international financial obligations of States on the full enjoyment of all human rights, 
particularly economic, social and cultural rights. 
</p>
<p> 
</p>
