 Jonathan D. Ostry, Andrew Berg and Charalambos G. Tsangarides, &#8220;Redistribution, Inequality and 
</p>
<p>Growth&#8221;, IMF Staff Discussion Note, February 2014.  
 
</p>
<p>49
